  21 Mar 2008; Markus Dittrich <markusle@gentoo.org>
  +files/gdl-0.9_pre6-magick.patch, gdl-0.9_pre5.ebuild,
  gdl-0.9_pre6.ebuild:
  Added patch to fix compilation issues with imagemagick-6.3.9* 
  (see bug #214040).

